Constructor Detail

FileModificationDateFilter

public FileModificationDateFilter()
Creates an instance of the FileModificationDateFilter class to filter files by their modification dates. Files can be filtered after a certain date, before a certain date, between a begin and end date, and on a particular date.

FileModificationDateFilter

public FileModificationDateFilter(java.util.Date after)
Creates an instance of the FileModificationDateFilter class to filter files by their modification dates. Files can be filtered after a certain date, before a certain date, between a begin and end date, and on a particular date. This constructor defaults the filter type to AFTER where a file's last modification must be after the "after" date parameter.
Parameters:
after:Ljava.util.Date - object specifying after this date.

Creates an instance of the FileModificationDateFilter class to filter files by their modification dates. Files can be filtered after a certain date, before a certain date, between a begin and end date, and on a particular date. This constructor defaults the filter type to BETWEEN where a file's last modification must be after the "after" date parameter and before the "before" date parameter.
